ZH: 我不慎打破了花瓶。
EN: I accidentally broke the vase.

ZH: 小狗不慎跑到了马路上。
EN: The puppy accidentally ran onto the road.

ZH: 她不慎在公司里摔倒了。
EN: She accidentally slipped in the office.

ZH: 我不慎将手机掉进了水里。
EN: I accidentally dropped my phone into the water.

ZH: 他不慎删除了重要的文件。
EN: He accidentally deleted important files.

ZH: 雨天路滑，容易不慎摔倒。
EN: The slippery road can easily lead to accidents.

ZH: 孩子们不慎把蜡笔画在了墙上。
EN: The children accidentally drew on the wall with crayons.

ZH: 路上行车时要小心不慎刮到其他车辆。
EN: Be careful to not accidentally scratch other cars on the road.

ZH: 奶奶不慎摔断了手腕。
EN: Grandma accidentally fractured her wrist.

ZH: 弟弟不慎溅到了热水。
EN: Little brother accidentally splashed hot water on himself.

ZH: 他不慎错过了重要的会议。
EN: He accidentally missed an important meeting.

ZH: 我们要小心不慎触动高压电线。
EN: We must be careful to not accidentally touch high-voltage wires.

ZH: 她不慎丢失了房间的钥匙。
EN: She accidentally lost the key to the room.

ZH: 学生们必须小心不慎在实验室里。
EN: Students must be careful to not accidentally cause incidents in the lab.

ZH: 我们应该避免不慎分享个人隐私。
EN: We should avoid accidentally sharing personal information.

ZH: 行走时要小心不慎滑倒。
EN: Be careful to not accidentally slip and fall while walking.

ZH: 不慎忘记锁门可能导致财产损失。
EN: Forgetting to lock the door can lead to property loss.

ZH: 不慎开车疲劳容易发生交通事故。
EN: Accidentally driving while fatigued can easily lead to accidents.

ZH: 小心不慎碰到火可以导致烧伤。
EN: Accidentally touching fire can lead to burns.

ZH: 半夜上厕所要小心不慎绊倒。
EN: Be careful to not accidentally trip when going to the bathroom at night.
